title: [P3D] A2A Cessna 182 - [Requested]
description:
100% working aircraft from A2A Simulation as a request for one of the users.

Tried it myself it's looks like everything is working. One of the best GA single-prop

aircraft out for P3D in my opinion. 

Correct me if i'm wrong but it doesn't need the A2A accusim core update for it to 

run. If it dose you can find it on A2A simulations website.




Of course feel free to comment if you have any questions or problems.

If you like this software please consider buying it !
